name: 10-20 Media
overview: 10-20 Media, Inc. operates online marketplaces for publishers, businesses, and brands. It provides a vertical marketplace platform that provides search solutions for local products and services, relevant content, and local business listings in the categories of home furnishings, home improvement services, and lawn and garden products and services. The company also offers a local advertising platform that enables businesses to place advertising messages in front of online home and garden audiences in the research mode. In addition, it provides a platform for brands to deliver product information to researching consumers with virtual product tags and product collections. Further, the company offers vertical search solutions for the Websites of newspapers, magazines, and television stations, as well as for specialty Websites. Furthermore, it provides Web design services for developing new Websites, refreshing existing Websites, campaign pages, online videos, and logo designs. 10-20 Media, Inc. was founded in 2001 and is based in Woodbine, Maryland.
